{"tid":2424660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張致恒扮著草避債 秘搬花園靚屋打的出入 債主Naomi：冇錢點會愈搬愈大","createTime":"2021-02-26T17:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T07:45:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"488c4350e0d7d4ce48b863320ce8f64d41bb85b2","tid":2424660,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T17:52:53.000Z","msg":"現年36歲的張致恒（Steven），上月被揭欠嫩模Naomi、阿Bob和張彥博的債 ，最近更有指在他的元朗村屋住所外，被貼街招追債，信箱塞滿追債紙張和信件，<br />\n<br />\nSteven連電話亦停用，懷疑潛水「著草」。<br />\n<br />\n但有讀者向《壹》仔報料，雖然Steven欠下一身債，但卻有錢搬新屋，而且愈搬愈豪，新居是靚裝新村屋，他住地下單位連大花園，識揀呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_777325_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_777325_0&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=33197f4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_777325_0&h=f97a9719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_777325_0</a>"},{"pid":"8e213f8850f813ec35757ae806ed89b4773e7fd8","tid":2424660,"uid":106,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T17:55:23.000Z","msg":"我憑自己本事借的錢憑什麼要還？"},{"pid":"8caadbf234293c48cfb3e04ad09b4374613e461b","tid":2424660,"uid":85586,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"阿偉啲同鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef54c2ebea292bf4214b00e18adfc43f56967abe","tid":2424660,"uid":85421,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T17:59:59.000Z","msg":"打乜撚野的？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97357409fb6384ce2b0c527d62ca053f2a696e5f","tid":2424660,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8caadbf234293c48cfb3e04ad09b4374613e461b","tid":2424660,"uid":85586,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"阿偉啲同鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\